Here’s a complete deep learning syllabus covering fundamentals to advanced topics.
It includes neural networks, CNNs, RNNs, NLP, optimization, and deployment—ideal for structured learning or designing a course.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
---

🧠 Deep Learning Complete Syllabus

#### 📘 **Foundations of Deep Learning**
- Introduction to Machine Learning and Deep Learning
- Difference between ML, DL, and AI
- Applications of Deep Learning
- Overview of Neural Networks

#### 🧪 **Mathematical & Programming Prerequisites**
- Linear Algebra: matrices, vectors, eigenvalues
- Probability & Statistics
- Calculus: derivatives, gradients
- Python Programming
- Libraries: NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib

#### 🔧 **Core Neural Network Concepts**
- Perceptron and Multilayer Perceptron (MLP)
- Activation Functions: Sigmoid, ReLU, Tanh, Softmax
- Loss Functions: MSE, Cross-Entropy
- Gradient Descent & Backpropagation
- Optimization Techniques: SGD, Adam, RMSProp

#### 🧱 **Deep Learning Architectures**
- Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs)
  - Filters, pooling, padding
  - Popular architectures: LeNet, AlexNet, VGG, ResNet
- Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs)
  - LSTM, GRU
  - Sequence modeling

#### 🗣️ **Natural Language Processing (NLP)**
- Word embeddings: Word2Vec, GloVe
- Text classification
- Sentiment analysis
- Transformers and BERT (advanced)

#### 🧬 **Unsupervised Learning**
- Autoencoders
- Variational Autoencoders (VAE)
- Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs)

#### 🧠 **Training Strategies**
- Overfitting & Underfitting
- Regularization: Dropout, L2/L1
- Batch Normalization
- Early Stopping
- Transfer Learning

#### 🧪 **Model Evaluation & Deployment**
- Evaluation Metrics: Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1 Score
- Confusion Matrix
- TensorBoard for visualization
- Model Deployment: Flask, FastAPI, Streamlit
- ONNX, TensorFlow Lite for mobile deployment

#### 📚 **Capstone Projects & Real-World Applications**
- Image classification (MNIST, CIFAR-10)
- Object detection (YOLO, SSD)
- Text generation
- Chatbots
- Medical image analysis

---

### 📌 Suggested Resources
- Book: *Deep Learning* by Ian Goodfellow, Yoshua Bengio, and Aaron Courville
- Course: [NPTEL Deep Learning](https://onlinecourses.nptel.ac.in/noc22_cs22/preview)
- Syllabus PDF: [Softlogic Systems Deep Learning Course](https://www.softlogicsys.in/deep-learning-course-syllabus/)
- Overview: [Collegedunia Deep Learning Syllabus](https://collegedunia.com/courses/deep-learning/syllabus)
